# Production build env (loaded by `vite build`, which runs in production mode).
#
# Channel Pricing migration — Phase 4 switch.
# When "true", My Rates / Rate Manager source the Booking.com Sell Rate waterfall
# from Channel Pricing (distribution_channel_pricing + overrides) instead of
# rockenue_managed_assets. Display + manual reverse-calc only — pushes nothing.
# Rollback: set to "false" (or remove) and redeploy. See
# claude/channel-pricing-migration.md Phase 4.
VITE_USE_CHANNEL_PRICING_SELL_RATE=true
